ğŸ Environment Setup
This project requires Python 3.11. It's recommended to use Conda for managing dependencies.

ğŸ”§ Create a Conda Environment
bash
Copy
Edit
conda create -n ml_pipeline python=3.11
conda activate ml_pipeline
ğŸ“¦ Install Dependencies
bash
Copy
Edit
pip install -r requirement.txt
âœ… You can optionally create a conda environment YAML file for more portable sharing. Let me know if you want one.

